SELECT PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYID, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYNAME, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.INTERNALNAME, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DESCRIPTION, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.VERSION, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.SOURCE, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.DISPLAYNAME as columndisplayname, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.TYPE, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.SEQUENCE, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.SORTORDER, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.SOURCE, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.DISPLAYID, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.DESCRIPTION as columndescription, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYID, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.RENDERTYPE, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.WIDTH FROM PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS, PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS WHERE PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYID IN (:"PSXSingleParam/inclausequery") AND PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYID = PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.DISPLAYID ORDER BY PSX_DISPLAYFORMATS.DISPLAYID ASC,PSX_DISPLAYFORMATCOLUMNS.SEQUENCE ASC

SELECT PSX_SEARCHES.SEARCHID, PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYNAME, PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYFORMAT, PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE, PSX_SEARCHES.CUSTOMURL, PSX_SEARCHES.INTERNALNAME, PSX_SEARCHES.DESCRIPTION, PSX_SEARCHES.VERSION FROM PSX_SEARCHES PSX_SEARCHES, PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW WHERE PSX_SEARCHES.SEARCHID = PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYID AND (PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE = 'Search' OR PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE = 'CustomSearch' OR PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE = 'StandardSearch') AND ( ':"PSXUserContext/ServerAccessRights/administerServer"'='1' OR (PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYNAME = 'sys_username' AND PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYVALUE = ':"PSXUserContext/User/Name"') OR (PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYNAME = 'sys_community' AND (PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYVALUE = ':"PSXUserContext/User/SessionObject/sys_community"' OR PSX_SEARCHPROPERTIES_VIEW.PROPERTYVALUE = '-1'))) ORDER BY PSX_SEARCHES.TYPE ASC, PSX_SEARCHES.DISPLAYNAME ASC
